These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: biathlon, weightlifting, sailing
1. Sport:weightlifting is on the right of Sport:sailing##1
2. Sport:biathlon is on the far right##1
3. Sport:biathlon is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | sailing | weightlifting | biathlon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: raspberry, lettuce, pomegranate
1. Food:lettuce is in an odd position##4
2. Food:raspberry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | raspberry | pomegranate | lettuce |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: rock-climbing, chess, reading
1. Hobby:chess is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:chess is on the left or right of Hobby:reading##3
3. Hobby:reading is on the right of Hobby:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | chess | reading |

 #################################
 
